Example Workflow
-->Using git fetch:

git fetch origin
git log HEAD..origin/main --> to check the changes made in remote repo, and compare the difference with local repo
→ Lets you inspect new commits before merging.
================================================================
-->Using git pull:

git pull origin main
→ Immediately merges remote changes into your current branch.

